Prerequisites

Python 3.7 or higher
Webcam
Windows OS (for voice alerts)

Step 1: Clone the Repository
bashgit clone https://github.com/yourusername/Driver-Drowsiness-Detection.git
cd Driver-Drowsiness-Detection
Step 2: Install Dependencies
bashpip install -r requirements.txt
Step 3: Download Facial Landmark Predictor
Download the pre-trained facial landmark detector:

File: shape_predictor_68_face_landmarks.dat
Link: Download from dlib
Extract and place in ./dlib_shape_predictor/ folder

Step 4: Configure SMS Alerts (Optional)
Get Free Twilio Account

Sign up at Twilio
Get your credentials from the Twilio Console:

Account SID
Auth Token
Twilio Phone Number



Update Configuration
Edit the configuration section in the Python file:
python# SMS ALERT CONFIGURATION
ENABLE_SMS_ALERT = True
PHONE_NUMBER = "+919876543210"  # Your phone number with country code

# Twilio Credentials
TWILIO_ACCOUNT_SID = "ACxxxxxxxxxxxxx"
TWILIO_AUTH_TOKEN = "your_auth_token_here"
TWILIO_PHONE_NUMBER = "+1234567890"
üöÄ Usage
Run the System
bashpython "Driver Drowsiness Detection.py"
Configuration Options
The system provides several configurable parameters:
python# Alert Cooldown Timers (in seconds)
EYE_COOLDOWN = 5        # Wait time before next eye closure alert
YAWN_COOLDOWN = 8       # Wait time before next yawn alert
HEAD_TILT_COOLDOWN = 4  # Wait time before next head tilt alert

# Alert Mode Selection
USE_STATE_CHANGE_DETECTION = True  # True: Alert on state change only
                                   # False: Use cooldown timers

# Voice Warnings
USE_VOICE_WARNINGS = True  # True: Voice alerts
                          # False: Beep sounds

# SMS Alerts
ENABLE_SMS_ALERT = True  # True: Enable SMS on first warning
                        # False: Disable SMS
Threshold Configuration
You can adjust detection sensitivity:
pythonEYE_AR_THRESH = 0.25           # Eye Aspect Ratio threshold
MOUTH_AR_THRESH = 0.79         # Mouth Aspect Ratio threshold
EYE_AR_CONSEC_FRAMES = 3       # Consecutive frames for eye closure
HEAD_TILT_THRESH = 30          # Head tilt a
